SELECT Sponsorships.sponsor_name, BrandIntegrations.brand_name, FashionShows.show_name FROM Sponsorships JOIN SponsorshipAgreements ON Sponsorships.sponsorship_id = SponsorshipAgreements.sponsorship_id JOIN BrandIntegrations ON SponsorshipAgreements.integration_id = BrandIntegrations.integration_id JOIN Partnerships ON Sponsorships.sponsorship_id = Partnerships.sponsor_id JOIN FashionShows ON Partnerships.show_id = FashionShows.show_id;
